data.title: Gabriella Wilde Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Gabriella Wilde with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Began her modeling career at age 14 after being discovered by Naomi Campbell

Appeared in campaigns for Burberry, Puma and Topshop before leaving the modeling industry to pursue a career in acting

Made her film debut in 2009 in St Trinian's 2: The Legend of Fritton's Gold

First appeared on TV in an episode of the BBC series Doctor Who

Is known to friends by her childhood nickname, "Bumpy

"
